## Usage in HTML

Images will be referenced in the HTML like this:
```html
<img src="images/hot-dry-noodles.jpg" alt="Hot Dry Noodles - Wuhan's most famous snack">
```

## Copyright Considerations

For a production website, ensure you have proper rights to use all images, either through:
- Original photography
- Purchased stock photos
- Creative Commons licensed images (with proper attribution)
- Public domain images